# Scratch verification harnesses (synthetic test fixtures, one-shot scripts)
.scratch/

# Large PDF binaries auto-committed into attached_assets/ (e.g. public filings) —
# block re-addition. Existing tracked PDFs are unaffected; gitignore does not untrack.
attached_assets/*.pdf

# Dev/verification P&L corpus — REAL financial statements (revenue, payroll,
# distributions). These are used locally to drive vocabulary-coverage and parser
# work and MUST NOT enter git history. README is committed as the catalog index.
fixtures/pnl-samples/*
!fixtures/pnl-samples/README.md

# Dev/verification rent-roll corpus — REAL tenant/lease data (tenant names,
# rents, lease terms, options). Same real-financial-data protection as the
# P&L corpus above. README is committed as the catalog index. Parked here as
# sample collection ahead of a future rent-roll ingestion pipeline — NOT
# part of the active P&L pipeline.
fixtures/rent-roll-samples/*
!fixtures/rent-roll-samples/README.md